text: Elina Gasanova (; , born 21 July 1989 in Baku) is a former Azerbaijani-born Russian tennis player. Gasanova has won 6 doubles titles on the ITF tour in her career. On 26 July 2010, she reached her best singles ranking of world number 581. On 24 August 2009, she peaked at world number 362 in the doubles rankings. Playing for Azerbaijan at the Fed Cup, Gasanova has a win–loss record of 2–4.
